 IR Sensor   | Arduino |
 ----------- | ------- |
 VCC         | 5V      |
 GND         | GND     |
 OUT (Left)  | A0      |
 OUT (Right) | A1      |

 Pin (L293D)  | Connection                                 |
 ------------ | ------------------------------------------ |
 1 (Enable 1) | 5V (or PWM pin for speed control)          |
 2 (IN1)      | D8 (to control Motor A)                    |
 3 (OUT1)     | Motor A terminal 1                         |
 4, 5 (GND)   | GND                                        |
 6 (OUT2)     | Motor A terminal 2                         |
 7 (IN2)      | D9                                         |
 8 (Vcc2)     | External Motor Power (e.g., 6â€“12V battery) |
 9 (Enable 2) | 5V (or PWM pin for Motor B)                |
 10 (IN3)     | D10                                        |
 11 (OUT3)    | Motor B terminal 1                         |
 12, 13 (GND) | GND                                        |
 14 (OUT4)    | Motor B terminal 2                         |
 15 (IN4)     | D11                                        |
 16 (Vcc1)    | 5V (Arduino logic supply)                  |
